data.value:
Tool to split and analyse RDI log files
1. Place the raw files under a root directory with folder names as COM01,COM02 etc for each Comms controller. 2. Select the root folder with the button to browse for directory 3. Run "Process Logs" to split files into seperate com ports 4. Tick the ports to be analysed 5. Run Calaculate Selected ports to totalise that selection
